Automatically switch to a new camera
Webex notifies you when a new camera device is available for use. If you prefer, set the app to automatically switch to use the new camera. Otherwise, you must manually select it.
Windows
Mac
Click your profile picture, go to Settings > Video, and check Automatically select camera on the Camera tab.

  This feature isn't available on Windows for Webex App.